== Documentation ==

The Genesi USA Efika MX Smarttop is supported on Gentoo, thanks to [http://www.genesi-usa.com/ Genesi USA] who provided us with hardware to bring this forward.

* [http://dev.gentoo.org/~darkside/arm/efikamx/install/ Documentation about installing Gentoo on the Genesi USA Efika MX Smarttop]

